    ns1:syllabusDescription "1. TEMA 1 Ground movements"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/1> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 1 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1.1. OPERATIONAL TOPICS. Airport markings and signs. Airport layout and areas. Ground equipment. Turnaround incidents. Start-up and push-back approval. Hot spots. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/10> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 10 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "4.3. LANGUAGE CONTENT. Verb forms: active and passive in the past; Use of infinitive and present participle- Prepositions. Fail to. Word stress and intonation. Describing incidents. Homophones. Enunciation, intonation and phrasing. Conditionals Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/11> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 11 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5. TEMA 5 Approach and landing incidents"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/12> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 12 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5.1. OPERATIONAL TOPICS. Expectation. Runway friction coefficients. Runway excursions. Stabilised approach. Loss of situational awareness. Approach hazards. Landmarks, terrain and obstacles. Jeppesen approach chart. On short final. Go-around Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/13> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 13 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5.2. CCCC COMMUNICATIVE FUNCTIONS. Correcting erroneous expectations. Asking about availability. Communication errors: uncorrected erroneous readback. Expressing concern. Describing precautions. Expressing urgency. Relaying information Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/14> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 14 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5.3. LANGUAGE CONTENT. Should. Giving advice using should. Will: future, intention and undertaking. Relaying information using reported speech. Describing position. Distance Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/15> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 15 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "6. TEMA 6 Handling a technical malfunction"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/16> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 16 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "6.1. OPERATIONAL TOPICS. ATC technical failures. Aircraft system failures. Consequences of a technical failure. Flight crew discussions. Electrical failure during approach. Monitoring a situation. ILS malfunction Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/17> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 17 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "6.2. CCCC COMMUNICATIVE FUNCTIONS. Summarising. Suggesting action. Communication errors: failure to request clarifi cation. Announcing a change. Self-correcting. Asking and answering about consequences and reasons Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/18> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 18 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "6.3. LANGUAGE CONTENT. Describing technical conditions. Talking about consequences. Phrasal verbs (1). Conjunctions and function words. Using context to distinguish between similar words Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/2> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 2 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1.2. LANGUAGE CONTENT. Easily confused words. Word endings. Interrogative words and phrases. Abbreviations. Using glossary definitions. American and British English Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/3> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 3 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2. TEMA 2 Communication on the ground"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/4> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 4 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2.1. OPERATIONAL TOPICS. Turnaround. Ramp safety. Handling incidents involving engineering, ambulance, security, firemen, tow vehicles etc. We¿re now at take-off. Managing a fire emergency Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/5> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 5 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3. TEMA 3 Environmental threats"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/6> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 6 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3.1. OPERATIONAL TOPICS Environmental phenomena. Pilot reports. METAR, TAF and ATIS. Weather radar. Effects on flight paths. Windshear. Responding to weather conditions. Icing. Volcanic ash clouds. Handling abnormal conditions in flight Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/7> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 7 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "4. TEMA 4 Level busts"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/8> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 8 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "4.1. OPERATIONAL TOPICS. Level bust situations. ATC abbreviations. Causes of level bust. Reasons for communication breakdown. Memorisation. Recommendations for pilots and controllers for avoiding level busts. Negotiating level changes Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/145017005/2025-26/syllabus/9> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 9 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "4.2. CCCC COMMUNICATIVE FUNCTIONS Reporting incidents. Communication errors: readback and hearback errors. Distinguishing call signs, frequencies and settings. Identifying causes. Managing separation and level changes Sin subniveles"@es .

